U7 chit8 e5 6 he3 gin2-na2 mia5 kio3 A-tin, u7 chit8 jit8 i theh8 chit8 e5 kiaN3 ti7 i e5 pang5-keng teh chio3 bin7 e5 si5, i e5 ma-ma tu2-ho2 tui3 goa7-bin7 jip8-lai5, i chiu7 ka7 i e5 ma-ma kong2, “Ma-ma, keh-piah A-bi2 e5 bin7 thai2 oe7 hiah sui2, li2 khoaN3, goa2 e5 bin7 hiah-nih phaiN2 khoaN3.”  
Ma-ma thiaN liau2, chiu7 kong2 chit8 e5 kou3-su7 hou7 i thiaN:
U7 chit8 e5 gin2-na2, i tak8 jit8 teh chio3 kiaN3, tak8 pai2 chio3 kiaN3 liau2 long2 chiong sou2 chio3 hit te3 kiaN3 siak hou7 i phoa3, koh chin siu7-khi3 kong2, goa2 e5 bin7 thai2 oe7 hiah phaiN2 khoaN3.  U7 chit8 e5-hng, i teh khun3 e5 si5, u7 chit8 e5 thiN-sai3 lai5 ka7 i kong2, Sio2 peng5-iu2, sio2 peng5-iu2, li2 na7 beh hou7 li2 e5 bin7 sui2, li2 tioh8 khi3 chit8 e5 chin chheng e5 chui2-ti5 hia, hit e5 chui2-ti5 si7 tui3 chia khi3, tit8-tit8 kiaN5, koh oat chiaN3-chhiu2 peng5 kiaN5, ia7 koh tit8-tit8 kiaN5, chiu7 oe7 khoaN3-tioh8.  Li2 kau3 chheng chui2-ti5 e5 si5 tioh8 thiau3-loh8 chui2-ti5 lai7, jian5-au7 koh peh khi2-lai5, an2-ni li2 e5 bin7 chiu7 oe7 chin sui2.
Keh cha2-khi2 hit e5 gin2-na2 chiu7 chiau3 thiN-sai3 e5 oe7 khi3 chhe7 hit e5 chheng chui2-ti5, i kiaN5 chin hng7 e5 lou7 chiah chhe7-tioh8, chiu7 beh khai-si2 chiau3 thiN-sai3 e5 oe7 thiau3 loh8-khi3, tng i beh thiau3 loh8 e5 si5, thiN-sai3 koh chhut-hian7 ka7 i kong2, “ChhiaN2 tan2 chit8-e7, li2 m7-thang thiau3 loh8-khi3, li2 to3-khi3 li2 e5 chhu3, chit8 le2-pai3 au7 chiah koh lai5, koh ti7 chit le2-pai3 lai7, li2 long2 m7-thang siu7-khi3, bin7 tioh8 siong5-siong5 chhio3-chhio3, tioh8 siong5-siong5 chhiuN3-koa, thiaN pa-pa ma-ma e5 oe7, koh lai5 e5 si5 chiah thiau3 loh8-khi3, an2-ni, li2 e5 bin7 chiu7 oe7 piN3-chiaN5 chin sui2.”
Chit e5 gin2-na2 thiaN liau2 chin bo5 hoaN-hi2, chiu7 to3-khi3 i e5 chhu3, chit8-e7 jip8 i e5 chhu3, khoaN3 tioh8 i e5 sio2-ti7 theh8 i e5 mih8 teh thit-tho5, i chiu7 chin siu7-khi3 phah i e5 sio2-ti7.  Jit8-chi2 tit8-tit8 ke3, i long2 boe7 ki3-tit thiN-sai3 tui3 i kong2 e5 oe7.”
Kau3 chit8 le2-pai3 au7, i koh khi3 hit e5 chheng chui2-ti5 hia, kau3 ui7 chiu7 beh thiau3 loh8-khi3, chong2-si7 thiN-sai3 koh chhut-hian7 tui3 i kong2, ‘ChhiaN2 tan2 chit8-e7, li2 m7-thang thiau3, li2 tioh8 to3-khi3 li2 e5 chhu3 tan2 nng7 le2-pai3 au7 chiah koh lai5, ti7 chit nng7 le2-pai3 lai7, li2 tioh8 m7-thang siu7-khi3, tioh8 thiaN3-sioh li2 e5 sio2-ti7, thiaN pa-pa ma-ma e5 oe7, bin7 tioh8 siong5-siong5 chhio3-chhio3, siong5-siong5 gim5-si, an2-ni, li2 nng7 le2-pai3 au7 lai5 e5 si5 chiah thiau3 loh8-khi3, li2 e5 bin7 chiu7 oe7 chin sui2.”  
Chit e5 gin2-na2 thiaN liau2 chin bo5 hoaN-hi2, chiu7 to3-khi3, tng i to3-lai5 e5 si5, tu2-ho2 i e5 ma-ma teh chu2 chhai3, ma-ma khoaN3 tioh8 i chiu7 ka7 i kong2, “Goa2 chhiu2 chin bo5 eng5, chhiaN2 li2 theh8 chit8 ki thng-si5 lai5 hou7 goa2.”  
Chit e5 gin2-na2 chiu7 bo5 hoaN-hi2 kong2, ‘Goa2 beh khi3 thit-tho5, goa2 m7 theh8 hou7 li2.’”
Jit8-chi2 ke3 chin kin2, chit8 jit8, nng7 jit8, chit8 le2-pai3, nng7 le2-pai3, chit e5 gin2-na2 long2 boe7 ki3-tit thiN-sai3 kong2 e5 oe7, tak8 jit8 long2 bo5 thiaN pa-pa ma-ma e5 oe7, phah sio2-ti7, koh gau5 siu7-khi3.
Nng7 le2-pai3 ke3 liau2, i chiu7 koh khi3 hit e5 chheng chui2-ti5 hia, tng i beh koh thiau3 e5 si5, thiN-sai3 koh chhut-hian7 ka7 i kong2, ‘ChhiaN2 tan2 chit8-e7, li2 koh to3-khi3 chhu3-nih, ti7 saN le2-pai3 lai7 li2 long2 m7-thang siu7-khi3, tioh8 choe3 koai e5 gin2-na2, saN le2-pai3 au7 li2 chiah koh lai5, jian5-au7 li2 chiu7 oe7 piN3-chiaN5 chit8 e5 chin sui2 e5 gin2-na2.”
Chit e5 gin2-na2 thiaN liau2 chiu7 siuN7, kiam2 u7 iaN2?  Na7 an2-ni, goa2 chit saN le2-pai3 beh chiau3 thiN-sai3 e5 oe7 choe3 koai e5 gin2-na2.  Tng i to3-khi3 chhu3-nih liau2-au7, chiu7 chiau3 thiN-sai3 e5 oe7, tak8 jit8 bin7 chhio3-chhio3, koh long2 bo5 hoat siu7-khi3, ia7 thiaN pa-pa ma-ma e5 oe7, thiaN3 sio2-ti7, i e5 pa-pa ma-ma khoaN3-kiN3 an2-ni chin ki5-koai3, si7 chaiN2-iuN7 i piN3 chiah koai, chiah iu2-hau3?
Chit8 jit8, nng7 jit8, saN jit8, chit8 le2-pai3, nng7 le2-pai3,......kau3 saN le2-pai3, chit e5 gin2-na2 chiu7 koh kau3 chheng chui2-ti5 hia, i kau3 e5 si5 chiu7 khai-si2 beh thiau3 loh8-khi3, hut-jian5 khoaN3-kiN3 chui2-lai7 u7 chit8 e5 chin sui2 e5 gin2-na2, i khoaN3 hit e5 gin2-na2 hiah-nih sui2, sim-lai7 chin him-sian7 koh chin ki5-koai3, thai2 u7 chiah sui2 e5 gin2-na2, tng i teh ki5-koai3 e5 si5, thiN-sai3 lai5 ka7 i kong2, ‘Sio2 peng5-iu2, chui2-lai7 hit e5 sui2 e5 gin2-na2 chiu7-si7 li2 pun2-sin neh.”   
Chit e5 gin2-na2 thiaN liau2 kiaN chit8 tio5, chong2-si7 sim-lai7 hui-siong5 hoaN-hi2, chiu7 koaN2-kin2 chau2 to3-khi3 in chhu3, theh8 kiaN3 tit8-tit8 chio3, tit8-tit8 khoaN3, u7 iaN2!  I e5 bin7 si7 hiah-nih sui2, ju2 khoaN3 ju2 sui2, i hoaN-hi2 kau3 thiau3 khi2-lai5, in-ui7 i si7 chit8 e5 chin sui2 e5 gin2-na2.
Tui3 hit jit8 khi2, hit e5 gin2-na2 siong5-siong5 ki3-tit thiN-sai3 e5 oe7, choe3 chin koai e5 gin2-na2, tak8 lang5 long2 o-lo2 i si7 chit8 e5 chin koai koh chin sui2 e5 kou2-chui gin2-na2.”
A-tin thiaN ma-ma kong2 soah chit e5 gin2-na2 e5 kou3-su7, chiu7 chai na7 beh u7 sui2 e5 bin7, tioh8 ai3 siong5-siong5 bin7 chhio3-chhio3, bo5 hoat siu7-khi3, thiaN pa-pa ma-ma e5 oe7, choe3 chin koai e5 gin2-na2, an2-ni bin7 chiu7 oe7 chin sui2.
（Lu2-soan Geh8-khan Te7 77 ki5, 1966 ni5 5 geh8)
